# APA App Commit Message Template
# Type: feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|perf|test|chore|revert|ci|build|wip
# Scope: ui|api|css|js|test|docs|build|ci|etc.
# Subject: brief description of the change
#
# Examples:
# feat(ui): add dark mode toggle
# fix(api): resolve authentication timeout
# docs(readme): update installation instructions
# style(css): format code according to style guide
# refactor(components): extract common button styles
#
# Body: (optional) detailed description of the change
#
# Footer: (optional) references to issues, breaking changes, etc.
# Fixes #123
# BREAKING CHANGE: description of breaking change
#
# Note: Subject line should be 72 characters or less
#       Body should be wrapped at 72 characters
#       Use present tense in the subject line
#       Don't end the subject line with a period

# Type: 
# Scope: 
# Subject: 

# Body:

# Footer: 